import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Header from './Header'
import PushOffCanvas from './PushOffCanvas'
import '../styles/Home.css'
import FlashBlock from './FlashBlock'

export default function Home(){

    return (
        <>
            <PushOffCanvas />

            <main className="pushcanvas-content main">
                <Header />

                <section className="d-grid gap-3">
                    <section className="carousel">
                    </section>

                    <section className="nav-cards">
                        <Container className="mx-md-0">
                            <Row className="gap-1 flex-sm-column flex-md-row gap-lg-1 justify-content-center align-items-center">
                                <Col className="mx-3"></Col>

                                <Col></Col>

                                <Col></Col>
                            </Row>
                        </Container>
                    </section>

                    <FlashBlock />

                </section>
                

                


            </main>

        </>
    )
}
